00:31:36.520 --> 00:31:39.750
If you only cry, you can't save your husband.

00:31:39.750 --> 00:31:43.690
Yes. Yes, I understand. Just please hurry!

00:31:43.690 --> 00:31:45.410
An ambulance is already on its way.

00:31:45.410 --> 00:31:48.450
However, we must administer CPR until then.

00:31:48.450 --> 00:31:51.740
