- Mikami-san, keep it up. You can do it!

00:33:03.600 --> 00:33:07.900
- One, two, three, four. One, two, three, four.
- Dear... Dear!

00:33:07.900 --> 00:33:14.390
- One, two, three, four. One, two, three, four.
- Dear, please... Please!

00:33:14.390 --> 00:33:18.070
Keep it up. An ambulance is on its way.

00:33:18.070 --> 00:33:20.150
One, two, three, four.

00:33:20.150 --> 00:33:24.480
One, two, three, four. One, two, three, four.

00:33:24.480 --> 00:33:26.840
One, two, three, four.

00:33:26.840 --> 00:33:29.820
You can do this, Mikami-san. Please proceed.

00:33:29.820 --> 00:33:32.410
One, two, three...

00:33:33.210 --> 00:33:35.650
Is that the ambulance?

00:33:35.650 --> 00:33:37.150
Yes!

00:33:39.270 --> 00:33:41.820
