00:34:32.670 --> 00:34:34.600
Sorry.

00:34:34.600 --> 00:34:36.600
Don't apologize.

00:34:36.600 --> 00:34:40.250
My daughter chose to marry a firefighter.

00:34:43.870 --> 00:34:45.820
So, please.

00:34:45.820 --> 00:34:48.480
Please save Shiori and Hikari.

00:34:48.480 --> 00:34:52.320
Please, I'm begging you.

