See, I live right next to the Ishikuras.

00:37:02.870 --> 00:37:06.860
- Got it.
- Yes, and their daughter and grandson are visiting.

00:37:06.860 --> 00:37:10.490
But a landslide hit their place earlier!

00:37:10.490 --> 00:37:13.760
The landslide in District 3 of Noharadai, correct?

00:37:13.760 --> 00:37:16.220
A rescue squad is on their way to provide assistance.

00:37:16.220 --> 00:37:19.480
Hatakeyama-san, hurry! Over here!

00:37:19.480 --> 00:37:20.980
Yes, I'm coming.

