The Ishikura house is the last we have to check.

00:37:23.900 --> 00:37:26.900
I'll head on over and see if anyone is inside.

00:37:26.900 --> 00:37:30.130
Ma'am, it's dangerous. Please stand back someplace safe.

00:37:30.130 --> 00:37:31.700
What are you saying?

00:37:31.700 --> 00:37:36.470
I've known both Shiori-chan and Hikari-chan since they were wee babies.

00:37:36.470 --> 00:37:40.900
I have to check on them. One moment.

00:37:44.950 --> 00:37:46.130
Hello?

00:37:46.130 --> 00:37:50.560
Shiori-chan! Hikari-chan! Where are you?

00:37:50.560 --> 00:37:54.340
I've come to help! Say something!

00:37:59.290 --> 00:38:02.290
Shiori-chan? Shiori-chan!

00:38:02.290 --> 00:38:04.600
There you are!

00:38:04.600 --> 00:38:08.400
Where's Hikari-chan? He's with you?

00:38:08.400 --> 00:38:10.320
They're both inside.

00:38:10.320 --> 00:38:13.740
It seems they're stuck in there.

00:38:13.740 --> 00:38:17.860
But I could hear their voices, loud and clear!

00:38:17.860 --> 00:38:21.750
Ma'am, thank you.

00:38:21.750 --> 00:38:24.830
But it's dangerous, so please stand back.

00:38:24.830 --> 00:38:27.700
There, I see the rescue squad!

00:38:27.700 --> 00:38:30.800
Are those... the Super Rangers?

00:38:32.080 --> 00:38:34.800
Yokohama Fire Bureau, this is SR Captain. Come in.

00:38:34.800 --> 00:38:36.300
Go ahead, SR Captain.

