And heave!

00:39:15.600 --> 00:39:18.100
Put your back into it, Hatakeyama-san!

00:39:18.100 --> 00:39:20.650
- Sorry...
- Again!

00:39:20.650 --> 00:39:23.900
Heave! Yes, they can make it through.

00:39:23.900 --> 00:39:26.800
- Ma'am, please stand aside. It's dangerous.
