Beware of any secondary disasters. Commence rescue!

00:39:36.330 --> 00:39:37.840
Yes, Sir!

00:39:37.840 --> 00:39:40.390
One, two, three!

00:39:40.390 --> 00:39:42.370
Entering building!

00:39:43.470 --> 00:39:45.160
Can you see the individuals inside?

