Both individuals have been rescued from the crumbled home.

00:40:09.300 --> 00:40:11.710
Isogo paramedics will treat them right away.

00:40:11.710 --> 00:40:14.170
This is Yokohama Fire Bureau. Copy that.

00:40:17.470 --> 00:40:21.800
They're both all right! Thank goodness!

00:40:21.800 --> 00:40:25.000
We have confirmed their rescue as well.

00:40:25.000 --> 00:40:29.220
Thank you for your assistance, Ma'am.

00:40:31.200 --> 00:40:33.000
Hello?

00:40:34.300 --> 00:40:37.660
Oh? Hello?

