Her leg was under debris for quite some time.

00:40:42.580 --> 00:40:44.100
Watch for crush syndrome.

00:40:44.100 --> 00:40:47.600
- Yes, Sir.
- One, two, three.

00:40:47.600 --> 00:40:50.200
- Are you all right?
- Yes, Sir.

00:40:50.200 --> 00:40:53.720
You're all right now, Ma'am. Great job holding out in there.

00:40:54.800 --> 00:40:56.500
Closing door.

00:40:58.120 --> 00:41:00.770
- Great work today.
- Likewise.

